per_agent.text:
[
  {
    "task": "Extract action items from the transcript",
    "owner": "unassigned",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "The meeting discusses the impact of COVID-19 on the tourism industry in Waikato, the response plan of Waikato Tourism, and the financial situation of Hamilton Airport."
  },
  {
    "task": "Review the financial situation of Hamilton Airport",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "The hotel has been impacted significantly as well. Fortunately during April we have was um uh taken over by Ministry of Health as a isolation facility."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a revised Statement of Intent (SOI) for the next three years",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "May",
    "evidence": "We have completed a very detailed 15-month forecast through to 30 June next year. That will form of course now part of the year one of the um of the SOI."
  },
  {
    "task": "Implement cost reductions in the business",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We've completed significant cost reductions in the business that's right across the business so that's um major cost reductions in our expense lines uh reductions uh pretty much across our business in terms of payroll uh anything up to a 20% reduction."
  },
  {
    "task": "Apply for and receive the government wage subsidy",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We applied for and received the government wage subsidy across the group."
  },
  {
    "task": "Work with the Airport Association to see what support is available for airport companies",
    "owner": "Mark Morgan",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "The Airport Association that we're part of is doing a major piece of work uh with central government to try and see what uh support if any there are for airport companies that have been significantly hurt as you know we are we are long-term infrastructure owners and that requires significant capital uh to maintain the assets."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a revised SOI for the next three years",
    "owner": "Peter",
    "deadline": "May",
    "evidence": "We are looking to be bolder, more disruptive to enable you to help you transform how you and other Waikato councils operate."
  },
  {
    "task": "Advance key strategic projects",
    "owner": "Peter",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "There are some key strategic projects which we'll be looking to advance as fast as possible and and you'll see those projects in the statement of intent."
  },
  {
    "task": "Re-examine work to see whether it should be stopped",
    "owner": "Peter",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "I've asked for a re-examination of some of the work that we're doing to see whether we should stop doing it."
  },
  {
    "task": "Consider introducing green financing or environmental bonds",
    "owner": "Andrew",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "LGFA has done a significant amount of work on that and we are intending to offer green financing to councils."
  },
  {
    "task": "Reforecast the financial report",
    "owner": "Nada",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "A huge effort has gone on right across some across council in the last um, in the last two or three weeks, um, to, um, yeah, to reforecast and you should see the results of that reforecast and you should have a obviously a quite a different, um, forecast column in the next, um, financial report you see."
  },
  {
    "task": "Monitor health and safety resources and processes",
    "owner": "Bev",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We do have a very small health and safety budget, obviously, um, but it it What this health and safety lead indicators shows you is that we, um, we pay an ongoing, uh, fee to the Waikato Occupational Health Consultancy who deliver our health monitoring services."
  }
]

